title: #92Noon! 11a Hour 11/03  - Joe O'Donnell, Kirk Cousins Press Conference
description: Wild radio VOX Joe O'Donnell joins the show to talk Phillies/Astros, Wild/Kraken, & more.  We take a listen back to Kirk Cousins press conference on returning to Washington to face his former team.
